maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Hey!
Pleased ter meetcher, girl!
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.note: tatalu lips has a more irish accent there than in teh common events

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Hi!
Are y'all inner'sted in plants too?
[nods]
Good gracious, girl!
Hi!
Y'all gave me quite the scare there.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: T'm'as bien filé les j'tons là.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Hittin' them plants an' all.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: En m'massacrant ces plantes et tout.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Shucks, 'sall good.
They got some mighty strange doohickeys inside, don'tcher think?
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: Elles ont d'ces trucs bien étranges à l'intérieur, t'trouves pas ?

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: [nods]
Well, Ah'm \c[3]Talatu Lips\c[0].
Talatu Lips
Ah've takin' a notion ta findin' an' analyzin' as many as ah can.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: Et j'me suis mis dans l'idée d'm'analyser tout ce que j'peux trouver.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: But that's turned out ta be a lot harder than ah 'spected.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: Mais au final, c'plus compliqué qu'ça parait.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: See, gettin' at what's inside seems ta only be doable by Seekers.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: T'vois, trouver c'qui a d'dans, y a qu'les \v[lore.title.seeker]s qui peuvent l'faire.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Ah can only collec' what they bring me.
Might y'all be inner'sted in givin' me a hand?
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: T'serais pas int'réssée pour m'filer un coup d'main ?

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Y'all already seem ta know the drill.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: T'as l'air d'jà connaitre le truc.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Care ta help me out?
[nods]
Much obliged, girl, that there's mighty kind o' y'all.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: J'chuis bien content qu'y ait des gens sympa comme vous, m'dame.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: First, lemme give y'all this here...
\v[item.285.name]
Talatu Lips
This handy li'l gizmo will help y'all keep track o' yer progress.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: Ce p'tit bidule va permettre d'voir où c'est qu't'en es.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Jes' keep hittin' them plants an' analyze 'em by gettin' them doohickeys.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: Tout ce qu't'as à faire, c'est continuer d'massacrer ces plantes et d'les analyser quand qu't'en récolte.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Y'all can check yer progress in the menu too!
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: T'peux aussi voir ta progression dans l'menu !

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Ah took the liberty of addin' mah findin's fer the \c[3]Alpha Ball Plant\c[0].
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: J'ai pris la liberté d't'ajouter mes trouvailles qu'j'ai sur la \c[3]Plante Boule Alpha\c[0].

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Jes' keep hittin' them plants fer me, a'right?
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: Continue juste d'frapper c'tes plantes pour moi, 'kay ?

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: [nods]
Alrighty, Ah'll be off explorin' fer more o' them plants.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: OK, moi j'vais m'faire un tour pour m'chercher d'autres d'ces plantes.

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Might even meetcher again along the way.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: P'être qu'nos chmins s'recrois'ront, qui sait ?

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: Once y'all're finished, come find me in \c[3]Rookie Harbor Alley Quarters\c[0].
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: Une fois qu't'aura tout fini, viens m'voir dans l'\c[3]Quartier des Allées à \v[area.rookie-harbor.name]\c[0].

maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.orig: [shakes head]
Well bless yer heart, girl, y'all come back if y'ever change yer mind.
maps/autumn/path-8.json/entities/429/set.text: Oh, sois pas d'solée, m'dame, c'pas grave. Si t'changes d'avis, t'as qu'a rev'nir, hein ?
